<paragraph id="3A4B5872932EFFB9CDD68571FEFCF906" blockId="1.[151,642,1623,1683]" box="[151,309,1658,1683]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">
(
<figureCitation id="A2CF44F7932EFFB9CDDE8571FECAF906" box="[159,259,1658,1683]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 22" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1821,1843]" captionTargetBox="[156,1436,197,1799]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1436,195,1799]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 22. Species of Argyrogrammana collected at the PNSD. 1 – 2. A. alstonii. 3 – 4. A. nurtia ludibunda. 5 – 6. A. pulchra. 7 – 8. A. bonita. 9 – 10. A. amalfreda. 11 – 12. A. physis phyton. 13 – 14. A. halli sp. nov. holotype. 15 – 16. A. celata. 17 – 20. A. gallardi sp. nov. 17 – 18. Male holotype. 19 – 20. Female (tentative determination). 21 – 22. A. aparamilla. Scale bar = 1 cm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233289/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">
Figs 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CD968570FECAF906" box="[215,259,1659,1683]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="1.73" valueMax="2.46" valueMin="1.0">1–2</number>
</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="A2CF44F7932EFFB9CC4E8571FEE5F906" box="[271,300,1658,1683]" captionStart="FIGURES 46 – 55" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1704,1726]" captionTargetBox="[152,1434,193,1682]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[152,1434,193,1683]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 46 – 55. Male genitalia of species of Argyrogrammana collected at the PNSD. 46. A. alstonii. 47. A. nurtia ludibunda. 48. A. pulchra. 49. A. bonita. 50. A. amalfreda. 51. A. physis phyton. 52. A. halli sp. nov. paratype. 53. A. celata. 54. A. gallardi sp. nov. paratype from PNSD. 55. A. aparamilla. Left to right: dorsal view of uncus, lateral view of tegumen, saccus, uncus, gnathos, valva and aedeagus, and ventral view of valva. Scale bar = 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233292/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">46</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3A4B5872932EFFB9CDD685C8FD24F8B6" blockId="1.[151,1436,1730,1971]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">
In 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CDF485C8FF25F94E" box="[181,236,1731,1755]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="2011.0">2011</number>
a single male was collected at the hilltop while resting on the underside of a leaf about seven meters above the ground, around 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CC3585EDFE59F96A" box="[372,400,1766,1791]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="18.0">18</number>
:00h. In 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CCAE85ECFDEEF96A" box="[495,551,1767,1791]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="2014.0">2014</number>
three males were collected in a same day resting on the underside of leaves in the same tree from the record of 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CF448400FDF5F8B6" box="[517,572,1803,1827]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="2011.0">2011</number>
around 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CFD98401FD7CF8B6" box="[664,693,1802,1827]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="16.0">16</number>
:00h.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3A4B5872932EFFB9CD868425FD69F826" blockId="1.[151,1436,1730,1971]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">
This rare species was described from 
<collectingCountry id="42E318E2932EFFB9CF2B8425FD00F8D2" box="[618,713,1838,1863]" name="Trinidad and Tobago" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">Trinidad</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="5E652583932EFFB9CF968424FC92F8D2" author="Smart" box="[727,859,1839,1863]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" refString="Smart, P. (1979) A new species of Argyrogramma (Lepidoptera: Nemeobiidae) from Trinidad. Aurelian, 1, 9 - 13." type="journal article" year="1979">
Smart 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CE638424FC92F8D2" box="[802,859,1839,1863]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="1979.0">1979</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) and further recorded in 
<collectingCountry id="42E318E2932EFFB9C9308425FADFF8D2" box="[1137,1302,1838,1863]" name="French Guiana" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="5E652583932EFFB9C8658425FE9EF8FE" author="Brevignon" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" refString="Brevignon, C. &amp; Gallard, J. - Y. (1995) Contribuition a l'etude des Riodinidae de Guyane Francaise. Le genre Argyrogrammana Strand, 1932. Lambillionea, 95, 393 - 406." type="journal article" year="1995">
Brévignon &amp; Gallard 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CC5A8459FE9EF8FE" box="[283,343,1874,1899]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="1995.0">1995</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). The Brazilian specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="FDF423F1932EFFB9CF828458FCF5F8FE" box="[707,828,1874,1899]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="alstonii">
<emphasis id="08808460932EFFB9CF828458FCF5F8FE" box="[707,828,1874,1899]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">A. alstonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have a dark orange color, like the 
<collectingCountry id="42E318E2932EFFB9C9B18459FA55F8FE" box="[1264,1436,1874,1899]" name="French Guiana" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
specimens; however, the light blue spot on the upperside of the forewing is larger than the 
<collectingCountry id="42E318E2932EFFB9C9C6847DFAE5F81A" box="[1159,1324,1910,1935]" name="French Guiana" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
specimen (
<bibRefCitation id="5E652583932EFFB9CDDF8491FE07F826" author="Brevignon" box="[158,462,1946,1971]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" refString="Brevignon, C. &amp; Gallard, J. - Y. (1995) Contribuition a l'etude des Riodinidae de Guyane Francaise. Le genre Argyrogrammana Strand, 1932. Lambillionea, 95, 393 - 406." type="journal article" year="1995">
Brévignon &amp; Gallard 
<number id="8C3C4A55932EFFB9CCD48491FE07F826" box="[405,462,1946,1971]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228" value="1995.0">1995</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) and the 
<typeStatus id="E54FE6D0932EFFB9CF778491FD55F826" box="[566,668,1946,1971]" pageId="1" pageNumber="228">holotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
